claims:
1. A vaporizing device, comprising:
a first housing removably attached to a second housing via screw threads;
at least one air inlet for allowing air into the second housing;
a battery in the first housing;
a vaporization tube in the second housing;
a heating element inside of the vaporization tube;
a liquid in the second housing;
the device having a central longitudinal axis, the first housing, the battery, the second housing, the heating element and the vaporization tube aligned on the central longitudinal axis;
